      "question": "Please introduce yourself.",
      "status": "ready",
      "level": "쉬움",
      "type": "기존",
      "answerKo": "",
      "answerEn": "Hi, my name is Minji. I work as a marketing assistant in Seoul. I usually describe myself as calm but curious. After work, I like taking a walk near my apartment or watching short documentaries. These days, I am trying to improve my English because I want to speak more naturally with foreign clients."
    },
    {
