      "level": "보통",
      "type": "기존",
      "answerKo": "",
      "answerEn": "I live in a quiet neighborhood near a subway station. What I like most is that everything is close, such as cafes, small restaurants, and a park. On weekends, I often buy coffee and walk around the park. It is not a fancy area, but it feels comfortable and convenient."
    },
